How to debug?

1. Google
Copy and paste error into Google. Someone has had your issue before. 
2. Ask questions in the forum (Tealeaf)
3. Use binding.pry
4. Paste Errors or problems in Gist
5. Rubberduck debugging. 
When you come across a problem - explain how to came to that problem to your coworker - Ms. Rubberduck. Even better, explain the problem to someone who has no programming experience at all. 
6. Step away from the problem.
